      • addModel

        public void addModel(MultiRCSBQueryModel subGroup)
        Method to add a new subquery. If the subquery has no query, nothing is done. If the subquery has the same QueryGroupConjunction as this query or only has 1 query, then it's queries and subgroups are added directly to this object, otherwise the object is added as a subquery
        Parameters:
        subGroup - The subgroup query to add
